---
title: Homestead Protein Shreds Stew with Brown-Butter Smashed Irish Champ
description: A comforting stew is always a welcome sight at the dinner table—especially when the weather is chilly! Accompanying this chicken stew is a heap of green onion-studded mashed potatoes, also known as Irish champ. We've amped up the flavour with a nutty and delicious brown butter!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-d-emince-proteine-maison-6ba4d2e3.jpg
